  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "UET and related AI literacy work offer three main reasons suggesting that higher TMT AI literacy positively affects a firm's AI orientation: influence of expertise on the TMT, decision scrutiny of the TMT, and power within the TMT.",
    "According to UET, the characteristics of executives who make up the TMT influence strategic decisions.",
    "Executives' expertise constitutes such an executive's characteristic in the sense of UET, which can influence the TMT's strategic decision-making (Fu et al., 2019).",
    "The higher the share of AI-literate executives within the TMT, the more cumulative AI expertise is present within the TMT, helping all TMT members to develop a holistic understanding of AI.",
    "Thus, with higher TMT AI literacy, spillover effects of AI literacy between the executives are more likely."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "Executives' expertise constitutes such an executive's characteristic in the sense of UET, which can influence the TMT's strategic decision-making (Fu et al., 2019)."
  ]
}